  <brief_title>Cerebral Blood Flow Effects of Resveratrol and Piperine in Humans</brief_title>
  <official_title>Effects of Resveratrol Alone or in Combination With Piperine on Cerebral Blood Flow Parameters and Cognitive Performance in Humans</official_title>
  <sponsors>
